<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Eger</head><p>Der Rat kündigt seine Gesandtschaft wegen Heinrich VI. Reuß von Plauen für Dienstag nach Martinstag an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_63" id="30v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_63_r2l13">Den von Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_63_r2l14"><expan>L<ex>ıeben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>ıben</ex></expan> vnd des edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ıch</ex></expan> Reẅſſen von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l15">Plawen des <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Greẅcʒ brıef in <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> geſant habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l16">Darinn er ſchreıbt / daʒ er auf den dinſtag nach ſand Merteinstag ſchıerıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l17">dıe ſeinen in eẅr ſtat gen Eger ſchıken welle <expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ſein meynung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l18">da ʒu ſagen / alſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vnſer <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / auf <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag auch ʒu eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l19">gen Eger ſenden ſein <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> da ʒu hören vnd <expan>eincʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>VV<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l20">daʒ vns darein ıcht fıel . daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag nıht <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l21"><expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> gut ʒeıt beuor ʒu <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l23">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l24"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> xȷ<hi rend="sup">M</hi> <expan>virginu<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_63" id="30v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und des edeln
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rewssen von Plawen des
                                <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Grewcz, brief in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> gesant habt, darinn er schreibt, daz er <app>
<note><q type="date">auf den dinstag nach sand Merteinstag
                                schierist</q>14.11.1419</note>
</app> die seinen in ewr stat gen Eger schiken welle,
                            <expan>unser<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> sein meynung da zu sagen, also
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir unser
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        tag auch zu ewch gen Eger senden, sein <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> da zu
                        hören und <expan>einczuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
                        aber, daz uns darein icht fiel, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag
                        niht <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> gut zeit bevor zu
                            <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> tun. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> xi<hi rend="sup">m</hi>
<expan>virginu<ex>m</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
